  "title": "Sales Executive (Signage & Signboards)",
  "description": "<h2>Job description</h2>\n<p>Apex Signages is a leading and rapidly expanding company specializing in innovative signage solutions. We pride ourselves on our commitment to quality, creativity, and customer satisfaction. We're currently seeking a dedicated Senior Sales Executive to help us grow our business.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle inbound sales inquiries</li>\n  <li>Process sales orders efficiently</li>\n  <li>Manage customer negotiations with professionalism</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain long-term relationships with customers</li>\n  <li>Meet and exceed sales targets</li>\n  <li>Generate new business from existing and prospective customers</li>\n  <li>Collaborate effectively with internal and external partners</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Academic qualifications are not essential</li>\n  <li>Fluency in English and Mandarin, both spoken and written</li>\n  <li>Proven experience in a sales role</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite (Word, Excel, Outlook)</li>\n  <li>Keen attention to detail and commitment to accuracy</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude and a strong work ethic</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary of $3000, plus monthly bonuses based on sales performance</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for professional growth and development</li>\n  <li>A supportive and collaborative work environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>At Apex Signages, we value diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive workplace. We encourage candidates of all backgrounds and experiences to apply. Join our team and be part of our exciting journey at Apex Signages!</p>\n<p>Job Type: Full-time</p>\n<p>Pay: From $3,000.00 per month</p>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Cell phone reimbursement</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Schedule:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monday to Friday</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Supplemental Pay:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Commission pay</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Experience:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Sales: 2 years (Required)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Work Location: In person</p>",
